-- Aditya Birla Nuvo May Bid for Evonik Black Carbon Assets, Standard Reports
-- B y   T h o m a s   A b r a h a m
-- 2010-11-10T01:30:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/aditya-birla-nuvo-may-bid-for-evonik-black-carbon-assets-standard-reports.html
 Aditya Birla Nuvo Ltd., owned by
the Birla Group, may bid to acquire the carbon black division of
Germany’s Evonik Industries AG, the Business Standard reported,
citing two investment banking sources it didn’t identify.
Evonik’s black carbon unit may be valued at more than $1.25
billion, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
